==Other information==
* At one point in Huron County&#x27;s Peru Township, (approximately 7 linear miles away from the confluence) the East and West branches are only separated by approximately . This is near the intersection of Johnson Road and Peru Center Road.
* An area near the confluence of Seymour Creek and the West Branch (on Lamereaux Road) is said to be haunted. This area also has history from the War of 1812 era. The Haunting at Blue Bridge

